{"tid":1326750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遊行小貼士","createTime":"2019-07-17T10:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T11:10:01.000Z","uid":62270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1f43cf86bb173fea22514bf9b0a2a0388f4855e8","tid":1326750,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:34:49.000Z","msg":"由於各區將舉行和平遊行，所以有少少建議比大家<br />\n<br />\n1.如果大家唔熟悉個區的話，建議早一兩日去行一次認下路，睇下邊條路線可以安全返屋企唔會盪失路<br />\n<br />\n2.因為人多既關係，認路其間可以睇下邊度有cctv(你知啦，咁多女士去如果比人非禮都知邊度有拍底可以做證據嘛)<br />\n<br />\n3.遊行時間咁長又熱，帶咁多水，野食等物資實攰死，不如早d係附近搵個locker放底d野先啦<br />\n<br />\n4.行完出晒汗，記得帶多件衫去換呀，最緊要搵個安全地方換唔好比人偷拍呀"},{"pid":"12aa7d652fd2355d0ee6aa880fd8af9bea71c623","tid":1326750,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab3dcd28773c21822856e52d23c00beef6c804d","tid":1326750,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:37:26.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"5a22e4458d88216bed834aa52e7306bf828ab099","tid":1326750,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:40:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9179cf7abaa9fb215fc2d6812931b0c61012fdb","tid":1326750,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:51:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e19c51ad5f23b85a30ca97c92616351f33a409c","tid":1326750,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:10:01.000Z","msg":"係冇人睇到定冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}